    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1892-03-16T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1892-03-16T00:00:00-05:00" n="433"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d433">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Señor <persName type="from">Hurtado</persName> to Mr.
                            <persName type="to">Blaine</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of Colombia</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1892-03-16">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 16, 1892</hi>
                        </date>. (Received March 17.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to acknowledge receipt of your
                    note of the 14th instant, which reached me yesterday afternoon, in time to
                    forward a copy thereof by to-day’s mail from New York to the minister of foreign
                    affairs at Bogotá, whose instructions I shall await respecting the matter
                    contained in your said note.</p>
                <p>Accept, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">J. M. Hurtado.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
